      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANOTHER LEHIGH (7) is yet to break through in 13 starts but has run a number of placings. Hit the frame again last start finishing second (18.61) at Wagga. Can find winning form. ZERO DARK THIRTY (4) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 400m behind Orana Willow (25.01) in a Maiden. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Has the ability to give this a shake. ACE TO BURN (8) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a nose second (19.86) behind Zipping Lainey at Gunnedah. Has good speed and can quickly clear the pack out wide. Bold showing expected. OSCAR PHOENIX (1) is a Ricky Brewer-trained newcomer by Barcia Bale out of Fernando's Charm. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
